output_list.criticism: The claimTile function has integer overflow vulnerabilities in the xCoord, yCoord, and gameNumber variables. An attacker can set arbitrary values for these variables, leading to potential loss of funds or manipulation of the game state.

The claimOwnersEarnings function has an integer overflow vulnerability in the gameEarnings variable. An attacker can set an arbitrary value for this variable, leading to potential loss of funds or manipulation of the game state.
